Description: The tidycharts package enables user to generate charts compliant with International Business Communication Standards (IBCS).
    It means unified bar widths, colors, chart sizes, etc.
    All charts are generated in SVG format and can be shown in RStudio viewer pane or can be exported to HTML output of knitr/markdown.
